	   <tr><td colspan=2>to Add to Iteck's Post, A Really good one to do is the Testament of Vanear Quest. Its Quite Simple, and you get a Great Wis Stat Item From it. I did the Quest at about lvl 20, and still use the item. The Link to the Page to View the Item is... <br><br><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=2336" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=2336</a><br><br>The item is called, of course, the Testament of Vanear. Its a Book that Fits into your Secondary Slot, and gives you +10 Wis +10 Mana, and Mana Preservation 1 (Worn). Very Useful, and at lvl 43, I still have it, and know quite a few people of my level that use it also. Go to EQDruids.com and look up the quest there, and it will tell you from start to finish what to do.Hope this helps.<br><br>P.S.&nbsp;&nbsp;Theres a guard in HPH that you have to kill that is stationed in the Bandit Camp there. He will con green to you at lvl 34, but he's (from what ive heard, not to sure of exact time) a 4 or 5 hour Spawn, so be Prepared to wait. <br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Tluadan Mudvayne&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>&lt;Evil Dynasty&gt;<br>53rd Season Druid</td></tr>
