	   <tr><td colspan=2>My Suggestion is to use one Hand Slash While your Still using your Weapon, because that is what your Epic is Classified as, so you'll be more accurate with your epic Item. Eventually,(about lvl 19 for me) you'll have yourself Weined off weapons, and using Just spells, cause the Mobs keep hitting harder, and you just dont keep getting enough HP to be able to attack a mob face to face. Ask anyone i Group with... I start getting hit by something, I Run like a little school girl with the Class nerd on her heels. <br>Another reason for this is because when youll Come across Items that have GREAT wis plus, and fit into the Primary/Secondary Slots, but are Not weapons (ie Cones, Books, Stines, ect.) Hope this helps.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Tluadan Mudvayne&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>&lt;Evil Dynasty&gt;<br>53rd Season Druid</td></tr>
